column2: # Join active nests with lagged weather
# Minimal, stable lag model (adds year to control for trend)
active_nests ~ lag_total_rain + lag_mean_temp + lag_mean_wind + lag_hail_days + year,

MASS::glm.nb(formula = active_nests ~ lag_total_rain + lag_mean_temp + 
    lag_mean_wind + lag_hail_days + year, data = effort_weather_lag, 
    control = glm.control(maxit = 100), init.theta = 326.427347, 
    link = log)
Null deviance: 178.543  on 31  degrees of freedom
Residual deviance:  34.066  on 26  degrees of freedom
